I had mistakenly assumed that [getOutputStream()](https://github.com/frohoff/jdk8u-dev-jdk/blob/da0da73ab82ed714dc5be94acd2f0d00fbdfe2e9/src/share/classes/sun/net/www/protocol/http/HttpURLConnection.java?msclkid=7d35d8d4a5f111eca568655e1b6b8665#L1240) in this  class would cache the outputstream returned but infact it returns an new output stream every single time.

